snippet.title: The Fallow City Launch Trailer | Available on Steam
snippet.description:
Get The Fallow City on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/3410980/The_Fallow_City/

#thefallowcity #astronixgames #horrorgame 

Shoot Zombies with different Strength and Weakness, do Simple Crafts and Upgrades, Fight Monsters, Solve Puzzles, get Haunted by Creepy Creatures and Experience the Story in this Indie Horror, Action-Adventure, Story game.

Media kit - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1YoY4wHrh7bw7ualseGo1dxEkqRVDZJzI/view?usp=sharing
